Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好擔心好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要安全歸來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 有誰會傳特別通訊的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我這樣說你會覺得我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果你平安回來的話 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往可以更進一步嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興 明人也有一樣的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人不可以這樣，請原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才荷梅就一直在呼叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於注意到啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當沒什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我準備了很多食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也用不著這麼多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流的廚師\N要能隨時應付顧客的點菜這是鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，我們是夥伴夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能辜負女孩子的期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真可恨，羨慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡白癡，全都是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新手的角色扮演嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢要我們穿這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這樣比較有作戰司令部的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是他個人的收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的作業也開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士正在分析觀測衛星送來的最新資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會得到最新的情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS隊開始脫離能源線有效範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
