Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞著營火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍個圈圈大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS是愉快的好夥伴
