Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也有他們的青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢呼喚著明日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀地高呼…
