Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上把敵人的影像傳過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洗車子 那是戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪你們不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兩世代前的陸戰主力兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 洋化點的講法是AFV
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠戰車來守住地面
