Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方也採取經濟的戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒友給我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該學著點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月跟明人趁現在快去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
