Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是再怎麼舊式的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集多數也是個威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然資料不足，但情況很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多糟?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，非常糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，可惡
