Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪費彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個炮戰模組是對付竹節蟲的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏交給涼子他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電瓶被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，可惡，可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人，冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣，滿意了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹節蟲開始動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於資料不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法確知微黑洞彈何時發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可以確定一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次受創將更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的微黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因飛出太空之後自然蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以受害只有最小程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定會在大氣中蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳確定不會有錯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人可也不是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個結果會變成怎樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨大的放射熱在一瞬間將都市蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃過這一劫的地方也會有強烈的迦瑪射線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰模式從A改成D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安歸來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回來可傷腦筋了 我們可動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，電瓶已經全給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑開得太過份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源跟彈藥所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後不准給我擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好神氣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什，什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來跟過去的玩具不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTI配備有吸著地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，我正在做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光，地雷還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的AESTI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰車車體底部是裝甲最薄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以瞄準備車身的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車身是指戰車的車體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是指船的船體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親吻眼睛，命中\N(音同親吻眼睛)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，諸君?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實地攻擊弱點就算空手打倒也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急連絡，趕快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要逃 可是小AESTI也動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 剛才狀況變得危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在竹節蟲周圍的空間重力波的變動增大中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及修理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去要怎麼向司令部報告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，非常謝謝您的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越緊急時愈是堅強啊 我們的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她對成員有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣直接衝到竹節蟲去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎 天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道，可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入苦戰啦，你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之大家是夥伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法，天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人負責直接去竹節蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們負責在這裏阻止戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼就是這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去收拾竹節蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們去收拾戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料 就算阻止她也不會聽的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在，走開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大戰車要這樣對付嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"輔助電池剩一點"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了，馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候不浪費子彈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，還是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說了不要浪費子彈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"可惜，補助電池用完了"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好幹得好，做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赤月，作戰終了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠來接我們那最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有許多枝節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過辛苦了，天河明人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想好下一本同人志的標題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用"男人的友情天地"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有純粹的情感沈睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容與淚水的數目就會漸漸增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時想要更像自我地去感受風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於其他人的我自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"很久很久以前"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，要我幫忙辦人氣投票?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"思兼這麼說過"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是湊小姐成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，小光的眼鏡也實在不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我是機械?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"還是人類?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，還是艦長的胸部漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡白癡…呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我投星野琉璃一票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"宇宙漫畫的決定版"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般，次回，機動戰艦撫子是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳本首籐剛志\N所呈獻的星野琉璃傳奇三部曲第二彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要大家一起投票·
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，大家一起看喲!
